Package cookbook

Class Cookbook

java.lang.Object
cookbook.Cookbook
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Cookbook extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a cookbook containing a collection of recipes. Each cookbook has a title and a list of recipes.
Author:
Stephen Schroer
